{
 "file": "_STG03_1.bin",
 "source_size": 41832,
 "built_size": 44124,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1262",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "太阳系统的展开、进展得怎么样了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86aeb72e941e929e7b4e989e7fa02e892e989e80ae7f2e7bde7dae7baef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1295",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反射镜已就位！随时都可以照射！",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef65ead7ef3ae7c5e834ef97e9a1ef2de840e7c4e7f3ea1aef65ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12cb",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12e9",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "姿态控制喷射器……联动系统正常",
   "zh_hex": "15ebbee994ea3fe8deedf9ef65e8c30909ef2eef30e941e929ef3befc700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1322",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目标！所罗门、宇宙之门！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efd4e96fef97e7fbe7ece90c02e8bee8bfe7cde90cef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1357",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "照射角已固定！反射镜联动正常！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea1aef65eb1aef3aeac0e867ef97e87cef65ead7ef2eef30ef3befc7ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1390",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "太阳系统、照射！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86aeb72e941e92902ea1aef65ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13cb",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！敌将是提安姆吗……真有两下子{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97e7e3e84ae7b6e821e7fce823e8020909e820e7cbe97def4de88600ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1402",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "右翼区块通讯中断！舰队那边没有任何回{00}应！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec50ec35ef35ec10ef59eb1bef4ee982ef97e7d4e7c9e7b7e899e7d8e7cbe89aefbcef5200e873ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1440",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联邦军的机动战士、已经爬上所罗门表面{00}了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2eefaae7e0e7b4e7e4ef30ef28ef6402ef3ae8b7ee5def4ce7fbe7ece90ce9e7e86200e7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14a1",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……阁下？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8d7ef4d0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14c4",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战力被打得七零八落……虽然遗憾、也只{00}能放弃所罗门了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28efb0e7f1e7f5e80aec45eb74ecafe92a0909e8b8e7efeba9ed6102e7c0ef3200e7c6e86ce938e7fbe7ece90ce7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14e6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "命令全军各自撤离、之后你们也立刻脱身",
   "zh_hex": "15e853e94eefb4e7e0e819efb5e90ae90102e7cde7fee7b8e7bbe7c0e86be91fe9e5e88d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x151d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！可是……阁下您要去哪里？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97e7c4e7b60909e8d7ef4de835ef2ae7ebe8ffef31050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x154a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要驾大扎姆、向敌主力舰队发起特攻！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae953efa5e84be82302efc1e7e3e954efb0e7d4e7c9e870e847e7cfef67ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1577",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……没想到所罗门、竟会如此轻易{00}地陷落",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d0909e7d8e7e6e7d7e7fbe7ece90c02ef2ce7e2e7f0e7cae990e96400ef63eaf9e92a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但我也是坚守扎比家传统的军人、绝不会{00}白白送死……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7db8be7c0e7b6eb80e8a8e84be825e7dfea38e929e7b4e7e0b402e91ce7b5e7e200e809e809e9baa70909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15af",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ff",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1622",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多兹鲁中将、就由我来护卫您",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e856e8a2ef4ee84a02e7c5e8a6efccefcfe8e0e9b2e8350000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是基尼亚斯的部下吗……可是、留下来{00}会死的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e829e896e7d6e7c8e7b4ef70ef4de8020909e7c4e7b602e98cef4defcf00e7e2ef6ae7b4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165d",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你又不属于宇宙攻击军、犯不着在这儿白{00}白送命",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8f1e7b5ea24e879e8bee8bfef67e7cce7e002eb0ee7b5e86def29e7b9eb7ce80900e809e9bae8530000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x169a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不。这绝非徒劳",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b503e7b9e91ce8f0eb02ec4a0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ab",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了成就该做之事、我已决意将此地作为{00}葬身之处！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae837e7c5e898e81ce7cdefb802efccef3ae8abef3ce84ae7caef63ef2fe7c100ee96e88de7cde903ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ed",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……说得好！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7ede80ae7c7ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16fb",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在就向敌本队发起突击！跟上、诺里斯{00}·帕卡德！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7c5efc1e7e3efa6e7c9e870e847e8b6e7ccef97e973ef4c02e972ef31e7c800ef4beb01e801e82cef9700000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x173d",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1768",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔——！区区这点攻击、能奈我何……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81debafebafef97ef35ef35e7b9e822ef67e7cc02e7c6eb2fefccefbc0909ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17af",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈哈！看到了吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97e7f6e7d7e7bae802ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17bd",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等大扎姆量产之日、区区联邦、转眼间就{00}能打垮给你看！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e826bee84be823e851ec05e7cde98a02ef35ef35ef2ed102e9c2e90be8fce7c500e7c6e7f5ed43e839e7b8e7f606060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1808",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "区区那么个大块头！休想让吉翁称心如意{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef35ef35e7b7e7bde828beec10e92e06e90ee7e6e7f9e7d9ee88ea01e82de7f0ef3c00060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x181f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要狠狠撞向它的侧腹！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2aec7aec7aecdfefc1e978e7b4ecaaecfcef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x184d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x188e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阁下！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d7ef4def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ba",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请您多加小心、多兹鲁阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae835e7e9e854e83ee82d02e7e9e856e8a2e8d7ef4d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18e3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿纳贝尔·卡多……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e882e857e7e1ef4be801e7e9090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1908",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也随您一同前往、阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0e9a1e835efb6e85def51e91102e8d7ef4d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……连你也来了吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86ee7b8e7c0efcfe7bae802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1938",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的！这所罗门、还真聚了一帮不要命{00}的蠢货啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b4ef97e7b9e7fbe7ece90c02e7f7e820ebe8e7baefb6e910e7b5ef2ae85300e7b4e94beaf5e7c300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1974",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阁下也是吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d7ef4de7c0e7b6e7d009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x199e",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼！也罢、跟我来吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b3ef97e7c0eaef02e973efccefcfe7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19d3",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……遵命！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ec40e853ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a05",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！那家伙、到底强到什么地步！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7b7e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4e8ade7d7e7dde7bdef63ea93ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a5f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快搬运物资！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fecdde986e99eeba7ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a91",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凯尔格伦的发进准备、还没就绪吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e95fe7e1e824ea5be7b4e870e892e87ae87702e7f7e7d8e7c5efeee802ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af1",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来您在撤离的准备上、费了不少周折啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe835ef29e90ae901e7b4e87ae877ef4c02e95de7bae7b5efacea5ced64e7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b23",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诺里斯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e972ef31e7c805000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b42",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基尼亚斯少将在何处？",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e896e7d6e7c8eface84aef29efbce903050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b6a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哥哥他、满脑子都只有阿普萨拉斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bce9bce80c02eb61eb67e886e840ef32e7cbe7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b7a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明现在、该让尽可能多的士兵撤离才对{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e82fef2902e898e7f9e8f2e7c4e7c6e7e9e7b4ef64ef93e90ae901e836e7be00090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bb4",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里就由爱娜大人指挥吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef31e7c5e8a6e8d5e7eaefa5efb2e8c0e949e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be1",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯。我不能让士兵们、陪着哥哥的偏执一{00}起送命",
   "zh_hex": "15e86503efcce7b5e7c6e7f9ef64ef93e7bb02ef42e86de9bce9bce7b4eb4de9fcefb600e847e9bae853000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c26",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……您变坚强了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e835e955eb80e8ade7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c32",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莫非是因为……动了情？",
   "zh_hex": "15eba0e8f0e7b6ef33e7c10909ef30e7bae88b05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5c",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c7d",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您这话叫人寒心。我诺里斯、也并非无情{00}无义之人",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b9e81fe8c1efb2ee0ee82d03efcce972ef31e7c802e7c0e957e8f0e7dce88b00e7dce8cee7cdefb200000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c9e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我看得出来、只要瞧瞧如今的爱娜大{00}人便知",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7f6e80aefbeefcf02ef32ef2aead4ead4e7f0efb9e7b4e8d5e7eaefa500efb2e8fae85a000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cda",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯待我如同生父、我却对他一无所知{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8eaa8efcce7f0e85def8de88802efcceadfe7bee80cefb6e7dce7fbe85a000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d10",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我吗？是爱娜大人的、父亲？",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce80205e7b6e8d5e7eaefa5efb2e7b402e888e89405000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d2c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我已经下定决心了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef3ae8b7ef4de867e8abe82de7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d54",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯？",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c805000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d75",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基尼亚斯少将得偿所愿……真是可敬",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e896e7d6e7c8eface84ae80aec09e7fbe9610909e820e7b6e7c4ee3800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d8c",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若爱娜大人所愿是让士兵撤离、那助她达{00}成、便是我的职责",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e8d5e7eaefa5efb2e7fbe961e7b6e7f9ef64ef93e90ae90102e7b7ea23e88eef2b00e83702e8fae7b6efcce7b4eda8eba600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dac",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看好了！这撤离的路线、就由我来为{00}您打通！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6e7c7e7baef97e7b9e90ae901e7b4e8d2e91602e7c5e8a6efccefcfe7c100e835e7f5ef59ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ddc",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、不但不逃、还敢迎面冲上来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302e7b5e7dbe7b5e8c202e7f7e8cde931e862e95eef4cefcf0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1def",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……简直可笑！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9abe875e7c4ea1cef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e1d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这所罗门、洒下的无数同胞之血……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9e7fbe7ece90c02e6aeef4de7b4e7dce914e85defabe7cde9f609090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e43",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用你的命偿还吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3e7b8e7b4e853ec09e7f7e7d0ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e86",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇啊啊！住、住手……求你住手……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea88e7c3e7c3ef97e85902e859ef660909e93ae7b8e859ef66090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ecc",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、简直不值一提！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302e9abe875e7b5ec48efb6e821ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f07",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "转眼间就被干掉一架……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9c2e90be8fce7c5e7f1e8d3e9d3efb6e99d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f14",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……简直是噩梦……这些家伙、到底是{00}什么来头！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e9abe875e7b6ed3fea400909e7b9e8a4e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4e7b600e7dde7bdefcfe92eef970500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f52",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f82",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "退下、卡多！",
   "zh_hex": "15e880ef4d02e801e7e9ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fb1",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就、就差一点就能突入敌本队了！区区这{00}点伤、算得了什么……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c502e7c5e9c7efb6e822e7c5e7c6e8b6e891e7e3efa6e7c9e7baef97ef35ef35e7b900e822e8f902e889e80ae7bae7dde7bd0909ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fdd",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2013",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、诺里斯中佐！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e972ef31e7c8ef4eefbaef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2044",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不必为我担心！区区这点伤、还不足以…{00}…！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e860e7c1efcce9fde82def97ef35ef35e7b9e822e8f902e7f7e7b5ea1ee7f3090009ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2067",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x209d",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽然很悲哀、可这……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7efe981e9dfecbe02e7c4e7b90909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20b3",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是战争啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6ef28e852e7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ed",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！是、是特攻吗……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b602e7b6e7cfef67e8020909ef970500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x212f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是现在！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2166",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多兹鲁阁下——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e856e8a2e8d7ef4debafebafef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2196",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多、多兹鲁阁下……！唔……怎会如此…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e902e7e9e856e8a2e8d7ef4d0909ef97e81d0909e7f2e7e2e7f0e7ca090009000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21db",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "成功了吗、阿姆罗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e837e9b1e7bae80202e7d2e823e7ecef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！就趁现在！全军、开始进击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e7c5e9eae82fef29ef97efb4e7e002e7fae908e892e7ccef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x222a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就这样、一口气拿下所罗门！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b9e7da02efb6eabde8ede9a7ef4de7fbe7ece90cef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2267",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2293",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……卡多大尉、你先撤退吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e801e7e9efa5efc602e7b8ef8be90ae880e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22c9",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯中佐？",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8ef4eefba050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f6",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "血路、由我来开！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f6e8d202e8a6efccefcfe7faef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x230d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快走、卡多大尉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fe89002e801e7e9efa5efc6ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2349",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什……！？竟、竟敢单枪匹马杀进来！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd0909ef9705ef2c02ef2ce8cde918eaaeed2ae84fe89be892efcfef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2387",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人的旗舰……拿下了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7b4eb0be7d40909e9a7ef4de7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23c5",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯中佐——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8ef4eefbaebafebafef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2401",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、出乎意料地不堪一击……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302efbee933ef3ceb8cef63e7b5ed46efb6e7cc090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x244c",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……阁下！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8d7ef4def97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2484",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么可能……！竟、竟然栽在区区一架机{00}动战士手里……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7c4e7c6090906ef2c02ef2ce7efec5def29ef35ef3587e99de7e400ef30ef28a5aeef310909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24c9",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人的旗舰……拿下了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7b4eb0be7d40909e9a7ef4de7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24fd",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行！根本来不及……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5efd6ef97e9b8efa6efcfe7b5e9cf0909ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x253c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "休想得逞——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90ee7e6e80ae9ebebafebafef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2579",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！所罗门陷落了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97e7fbe7ece90ceaf9e92ae7baef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25a5",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多兹鲁中将壮烈战死、麾下主要将官也尽{00}数……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e856e8a2ef4ee84aed47eaecef28ef6a02ec01ef4de954ef2ae84aef92e7c0e8f200e914090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25df",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……大佐！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa5efbaef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2602",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……如今、可不能再这样磨蹭下去了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7f0efb902e7c4e7b5e7c6e80be7b9e7daec81ec98ef4de7ebe7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2617",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛利根、联络西玛中佐！我军全速驶向所{00}罗门！",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e82ee9b802ef2eeb14e7f8e845c0a3068be7e0bbe9dae9759de7fb00e7ece90c060000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2650",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、遵命！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602ec40e853ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2679",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是要去救出留在所罗门的士兵们吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef2ae7ebe8caefbee98cef29e7fbe7ece90ce7b4ef64ef93e7bbe7d0ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2692",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！轮机全速！火速赶往所罗门！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97ebf4e7e4efb4e9daef97e8dae9daea04e911e7fbe7ece90cef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26bf",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "卡多！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e801e7e9ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26e1",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凯利、你竟然平安无事！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e95fe82e02e7b8ef2ce7efe887e7fce7dca9060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x270b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你才是！在那种绝境下、竟还能捡回一条{00}命",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e836e7b6ef97ef29e7b7e7d1e91ceb81ef4d02ef2ce7f7e7c6ecdbef52efb6e9d400e8530000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2741",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是啊。我苟且偷生至今、丢尽了脸面……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c303efccee94e999ebb4ef8de897efb902ebb0e8f2e7baeb69e8620909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x277d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "卡多……",
   "zh_hex": "15e801e7e909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x279f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别担心、凯利",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e9fde82d02e95fe82e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27aa",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯中佐救下的这条命、我绝不会白白{00}挥霍",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8ef4eefbae8caef4de7b4e7b9e9d4e85302efcce91ce7b5e7e2e809e80900e949ebfe000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27c8",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要守住友军的士兵、无论如何也要让他{00}们从所罗门撤离……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae8a8e859e960e7e0e7b4ef64ef9302e7dce8dce7f0efbce7c0ef2ae7f9e80c00e7bbe88ae7fbe7ece90ce90ae90109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27e7",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕赌上性命！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958ed0aef4ce951e853ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2813",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……那么、卡多、我这条命也一并托{00}付给你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e7b7e7bd02e801e7e902efcce7b9e9d4e853e7c0efb6e957e7f400e97ee839e7b80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2848",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凯利？可你、伤成这副模样……",
   "zh_hex": "15e95fe82e05e7c4e7b802e8f9e837e7b9ecb6ea91e7da0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2877",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你都拼上性命去战、我岂能躺在病床上干{00}等着！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e840ea66ef4ce951e853e7ebef2802efcceac3e7c6eff5ef29ed8be6baef4ce8d300e826e86def97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x289d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "区区断了一条手臂、根本算不了什么！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef35ef35e982e7baefb6e9d4ef66ee9202e9b8efa6e889e7b5e7bae7dde7bdef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28d4",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凯利……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e95fe82e09090600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2948",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『怎么会……诺里斯他！？』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7f2e7bde7e20909e972ef31e7c8e80cef97050d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x297e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『是、他走得无比壮烈……』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7b602e80ce890e80ae7dce825ed47eaec09090d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29bc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『诺里斯……』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce972ef31e7c809090d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a04",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（诺里斯……是我害死了他……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee972ef31e7c80909e7b6efcce988ef6ae7bae80c0909ef8f000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a34",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……爱娜大人、基尼亚斯少将有请",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8d5e7eaefa5efb202e829e896e7d6e7c8eface84ae7cbe83a000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a6f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a7a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请转告他、我马上就去",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae9c2e8e5e80c02efcce84fef4ce7c5e7eb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aa3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2adc",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae3",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（我不会……让你独自一人赴死！）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8eefcce7b5e7e20909e7f9e7b8e8eeefb5efb6efb2eb1cef6aef97ef8f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b0c",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b44",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯中佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8ef4eefbaef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b71",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哦、是卡多大尉啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e91902e7b6e801e7e9efa5efc6e7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b88",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无妨、别担心、区区这点伤、不碍事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce97f02e7e5e9fde82d02ef35ef35e7b9e822e8f902e7b5e8c6efb80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bc8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺里斯中佐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e972ef31e7c8ef4eefba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bf6",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个、贵官还是回去守护多兹鲁阁下{00}吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e82802e9308fe7f7e7b68ce7ebe8a8e8e0e7e9e856e8a2e8d78900e7d009090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c3c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！那是！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b7e7b6ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ec2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看我的！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcce7b4ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f02",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么可能……！竟、竟然栽在区区一架机{00}动战士手里……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7c4e7c6090906ef2c02ef2ce7efec5def29ef35ef3587e99de7e400ef30ef28a5aeef310909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f4a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f67",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "休想得逞！绝不让你得逞——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90ee7e6e80ae9ebef97e91ce7b5e7f9e7b8e80ae9ebebafebafef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fae",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "岂容你这区区一架机动战士、夺走吉翁的{00}荣光！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eac3ed2fe7b8e7b9ef35ef3587e99de7e4ef30ef28a502ea17e890e7d9ee88e7b400eb19e83d0606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ff8",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这家伙到底是什么人……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e7dfe7fde7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bdefb20909ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x902b",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要我在、就休想……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aefccef2902e7c5e90ee7e609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x906e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这家伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x909a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不能让友军倒下！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c6e7f9e960e7e0e848ef4def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90de",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、绝不会死！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e91ce7b5e7e2ef6aef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90f3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要活下去……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae8d4ef4de7eb0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x912a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要活着、和爱娜相守一生！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae8d4e86d02e7d3e8d5e7eae8b1e8a8efb6ef8def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9160",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？你就是爱娜大人的……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705e7b8e7c5e7b6e8d5e7eaefa5efb2e7b40909050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x91b9",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能见到爱娜大人的意中人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e85ce7d7e8d5e7eaefa5efb2e7b4ef3cef4eefb2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x91d5",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一生、过得当真有趣……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6ef8d02ef36e80aef53e820e7cbea8209090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9206",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是想从中阻挠吗……那就先送你上路！{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7e6e88ac0e8efed66e8020909e7b7e7c5b8e9bae7b8b2e8d2060006000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x929e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92ab",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』、一直玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160d02efb6e875e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92cb",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、在此暂告一{00}段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02ef29e7cae9ffe8e5efb600ea6be92a090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92ea",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、往后也希望你能{00}尽兴游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c600e8f2eabaea94e9700000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x930f",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为一路通关的你、我们还准备了特{00}别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1efb6e8d2ef59e8bbe7b4e7b802efcce7bbe7f7e87ae877e7bae7cf00e7e5e8bbe8010000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9336",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头作战的大天使队、进行的{00}特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92eef2fef28e7b4bee844e83fe7c902e8929fe7b400e7cfe7e5ea2feab600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9357",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}、想必也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c90002e7e6e860e7c0e7b5e8850000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x937c",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bb87e8abe8128900000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x93a1",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x93c5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也请你、尽情地玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b802e8f2e88bef63e970e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x943e",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路陪着我这个不太可靠的舰长、真的谢{00}谢你",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef3402e820e7b4e8b200e8b2e7b8000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x945d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x947b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束了{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895e7ba000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9495",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可游戏本身仍能继续、往后也请你接{00}着尽情游玩哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c6e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e83ae7b8efce00e86de8f2e88bea94e970e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x94bb",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为将这条路线玩到最后的你、我们还准备{00}了新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e84ae7b9e9d4e8d2e916e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802efcce7bbe7f7e87ae87700e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe801e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x94df",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是和我们分头、与提坦斯及新吉翁作战{00}的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7d38be7bbcde92e02e832e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88ef2fef2800e7b4090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x94fa",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x950d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能与{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e83200e80ce7bbe861ef28e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9533",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你务必去挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8e94fe860e7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9541",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9565",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲破重围吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef6de8a1e9dee7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x95e6",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x95f6",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我、向你一路以来出色的指{00}挥致以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b029de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c000e949ea32e7f3ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9618",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏贵官的协力、我们才得以一路奋战到{00}最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e930ef92e7b4e8f6efb002efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3efb6e8d2ef46ef28e7d700e8c5e7fe00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x963a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9650",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我们主天使队的战斗、虽然到此结{00}束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e8b8e7efe7d7e7cae86800e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9669",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、往后也希望你能尽{00}兴游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6e8f200eabaea94e97000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x968d",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战往后仍可继续、而且选择『特别{00}演习』、便能……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28e911e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e89ce999e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e500ea2feab60d02e8fae7c60909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96b8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab6000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96d6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以贵官的本事、与他们一战也定{00}能克敌制胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e7f3e930ef92e7b4efa6efb802e832e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7c0e86700e7c6e7d5e7e3e8dee8db0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96fb",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x971f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "愿你今后继续奋战",
   "zh_hex": "15e961e7b8efb9e7fee9d6e9adef46ef28000000"
  }
 ]
}
